'''Justice Systems''' was a company set up during the rule of the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] that manufactured the [[EverAlert droid]]. This [[Droid/Legends|droid]] was similar in many respects to the [[YVH 1]] [[Battle droid/Legends|combat droid]] produced by [[Tendrando Arms]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

